      <title>记录下二叉树的高度求法</title>
      <link>http://barbery.me/post/2012-12-08-%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%8B%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%89%E6%A0%91%E7%9A%84%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%E6%B1%82%E6%B3%95/</link>
